name: God of War Mint Pass Official

metadata.name: Mint Pass #1
metadata.description:
Critically acclaimed God of War combines with Metaverse.  
Mint will be live from Nov 7, two days before official game launch.  
NFT Holders will get God of War Ragnarok Digital Deluxe Edition with various benefits.  
Visit Site, mint free with Mint Pass and start the journey to the Nine Realms; save the world.
